column30:
Hiv and malaria kills almost quadruple the number of people covid kills per day, stop acting as if covid is the biggest problem we are facing, no record of covid by anyone during the end Sars protest all over Nigeria will tell you that a lock down is pointless.

Let us pay for our covid treatment like any other sickness, so people know there is a cost for getting covid that is more expensive than a nose mask. 

Tell the elderly to stay indoors and any body prone to do like wise, continue to inform us on how to stay safe, but also retain our freedom of movement, let anybody who catches covid pay the price for his/her treatment, because nobody gets covid by mistake if you follow the guidelines, so it's purely because of disobedience and disregard, and he/she should be responsible for it, that is what comes with having your freedom, responsibility.
